&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;各位同学好！欢迎大家本学期选修王英老师开设的《词汇的力量》课程，下面有几点通知请大家注意：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;一. 由于合班缘故，各位同学网络学堂上显示的&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;课序号均为&lt;b&gt;91班&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;，但请大家按照&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;选课的&lt;b&gt;课表时间&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;去教室上课。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;分班具体信息如下：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;周二91（二/3）、92（二/4），上课地点：六教6B312，助教：夏一纯； &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;周三93（三/3）、94（三/4），上课地点：六教6B312，助教：巴音；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;周五95（五/3）、96（五/4），上课地点：六教6B312，助教：齐宇。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;二.为方便课程教学，每名同学须加入&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;两个微信群&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;由91-96班共6个班组成的&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;大课程群&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;（群名：&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;26&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;春91-96班&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;）。本群主要用于发布重要通知、分享课程资料以及解答同学们针对课程内容提出的问题（可由其他同学先解答；若无人回答，最后由王老师解答）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;【注意1】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;由于该群人数庞大，大家进群需要有人邀请才能进群。大家可以先进班级群，然后找&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;各班级助教拉入大群&lt;/span&gt;或者已经在&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;大群的同学相互拉一下新同学&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:yellow; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;班级群&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;由同一天上课的2个小班组成&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;：周二91-92班群（群名：&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;26&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;春91-92班&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;；助教：夏一纯）；周三93-94班群（群名：&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;26&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;春93-94班&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;；助教：巴音）；周五95-96班群（群名：&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;26&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;春95-96班&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;；助教：齐宇）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;【注意2】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;群二维码&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;和&lt;b&gt;助教的微信名片见附件&lt;/b&gt;。群二维码过期会失效，请同学们尽快进群以免错过重要通知，后续二维码失效请联系各班助教。同学们加入&lt;b&gt;大群&lt;/b&gt;和&lt;b&gt;自己班级的小群&lt;/b&gt;即可，不要进错群，如调整班级需从原班级群退出再进入其他的班级群。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;【注意3】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;重要的通知内容会同时发布在&lt;b&gt;课程大群&lt;/b&gt;，&lt;b&gt;班级群&lt;/b&gt;和&lt;b&gt;网络学堂&lt;/b&gt;的&lt;b&gt;课程公告&lt;/b&gt;里，请同学们务必认真阅读。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;三&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;本课程&lt;span style=&quot;background:red&quot;&gt;不开腾讯会议&lt;/span&gt;。同学们因故不能到教室上课请提供相关证明。&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;因公&lt;/span&gt;缺课请出示盖有相关单位红章的&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;请假条&lt;/span&gt;，上面须有相关单位负责人的姓名和手机号码。&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;因病&lt;/span&gt;缺课请出示&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;医院诊断证明&lt;/span&gt;或缺课当天&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;校医院开药处方以及缴费证明&lt;/span&gt;）。&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;因其他私&lt;/span&gt;人原因&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;缺课一次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;扣5分&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;，&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;缺课二次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;请退课&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;【注意4】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;因选课原因需要串班上课的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;同学，请与王老师和助教协商后在&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;固定的班级上课&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;四&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;.&lt;a rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:lime&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;要想在本门课上取得好成绩，认真学习课程材料、做好笔记、按时且高质量完成各项作业是关键&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;。王老师每周在网络学堂发布的&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;课程课后（包括预习）作业&lt;/span&gt;需要同学们&lt;span style=&quot;background:red&quot;&gt;在上完当周的课后完成&lt;/span&gt;，例如： &lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;Homework for Week 1&lt;/span&gt;。该项作业需要大家在第一周上完课后、第二周上课之前完成。每周作业设定的作业完成截止日期（DDL）已经充分考虑到大家的各种情况，所以请同学们一定按时完成作业并提前预习以期达到本课程预期的最佳学习效果。如果无法达到相关要求请及时退课。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;【注意5】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;从本学期开始，本课程&lt;span style=&quot;background:red&quot;&gt;将不允许同学补做作业&lt;/span&gt;，请大家谅解（一般情况下，接近期末时老师和助教会给大家提供补做作业的机会）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;上学期有同学因未完成相关作业导致成绩不及格，请大家不要效仿。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#444444&quot;&gt;五&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none windowtext 1.0pt; background:white; padding:0cm&quot;&gt;开学需要&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;收取材料费20元&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;，具体收取时间和方式详见各班助教安排。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:24.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Monotype Corsiva&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:red&quot;&gt;Previewing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;Teaching at Tsinghua for well over 30 years, there are so many things I like about Tsinghua students, and of course there are quite a few things I don&#39;t like about them. And you know what I hate most about some Tsinghua students? At the top of the list&amp;nbsp;are definitely those who show up for a class for no other reason than to secure only a high score or 2 credits. If this is why you registered for my class, I strongly recommend you drop it at the beginning of the upcoming&amp;nbsp;semester when you can, because no freeloaders, never, ever, could make it to the end of the term.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:red&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;Please!!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;Speaking of study skills, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:red&quot;&gt;previewing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is always an important learning strategy. The 2025~2026 spring semester is about to start one week from now.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Are you ready? And this is where you&rsquo;re supposed to get started: Please preview and get ready for Week 1 &amp;amp; Week 2 classes: 1) Study Chapters 3 ~ 7(P), Word Power Made Easy (WPME for short); 2) Study Chapters 1 ~ 5, Unit 1, Vocabulary Workbook IV (12,000+ word level); 3) Listen to one of the two Cambridge English Readers Stories: 1. This Time It&#39;s Personal (&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:red&quot;&gt;the summary of which is due in Week 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;). The above mentioned course materials/textbooks (PDF) will soon be available in the course files under correspondent titles for you to (listen to or) study ahead of course schedule throughout the upcoming semester.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:yellow&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:red&quot;&gt;There will be a test the first week&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt; on the above-mentioned items 1) Ch. 3 ~ Ch. 7, WPME &amp;amp; 2) Unit 1, Voc. Workbook IV (12,000+) to find out how good an autonomous learner you are and of course your English proficiency level, too! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;Studying the course materials beforehand is very important if you want to hold on to the class till the end of the semester. Hopefully you can!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; 
